keylogger: Inject a keystroke logger into a process
steal_token: Steal access token from a process
kerberos_ticket_dump: Dump kerberos tickets from this session (base64)
kerberos_ticket_purge: Purge kerberos tickets from this session
usemodule: Loads and exec functions from powershell scripts (job)
push_agent: Push agent into proxy (param: proxy port)
proxy_reset: Reset all agents linked with proxy
proxy_link: Get all linked proxy<->agent (param: proxy port)
link_proxy: Get all linked proxy<->agent (param: proxy port)
